                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner on the 17th of February.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I never had any breeches in my possession in my life.</p>
               <p>MR. KIRBY. I am certain she is the woman; she was a regular customer at our house.</p>
